 />\n大家都無割<br />\n無理由小小事就分化掛<br />\n香港人唔好俾人睇唔起<br />\n唔好俾對家笑到最後"},{"pid":"7d0ed1443fa7e1d00b283f0d9f8c6c96daae4d87","tid":1466153,"uid":53254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:46:02.000Z","msg":"認真學下人地<br />\n<br />\n假料全心全意信<br />\n做柒事支持<br />\n做錯事撐<br />\n轉個頭面不改容出翻黎<br />\n所以先至一路咁團結<br />\n<br />\n我地不割唔係口講 OK"},{"pid":"bb4551d67d29b08839b3fec9817d966eba442413","tid":1466153,"uid":4352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e3fb4f8eaa2a455d5b1951860a806f52329d678","tid":1466153,"uid":134134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:45:02.000Z","msg":"鬼一定捉唔哂，一齊諗點做靚佢。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:46:41.000Z","msg":"講明係鬼<br />\n一個人好難處理<br />\n只有團結先可以解決問題"},{"pid":"e7cad8139e71499e301bfbdf4daa353be684ff56","tid":1466153,"uid":276527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:47:19.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"1b546dae6ae4a8395eb9d12a047c2a14c012181c","tid":1466153,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:47:39.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我理解前線情緒<br />\n所以我點都唔會割<br />\nthe revolution must go on</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"be3924bfb8d265a2cff0a03c25652f1d4a15caef","tid":1466153,"uid":4352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d0ed1443fa7e1d00b283f0d9f8c6c96daae4d87","tid":1466153,"uid":53254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:46:02.000Z","msg":"認真學下人地<br />\n<br />\n假料全心全意信<br />\n做柒事支持<br />\n做錯事撐<br />\n轉個頭面不改容出翻黎<br />\n所以先至一路咁團結<br />\n<br />\n我地不割唔係口講 OK"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:47:54.000Z","msg":"岩架<br />\n勇武和理都係為件事<br />\n大家做咩都支持<br />\n同路人呀"},{"pid":"0feee6945735d59dd7a51af6f0f5464b402f617e","tid":1466153,"uid":87735,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:47:57.000Z","msg":"聽日唔好塞機場住<br />\narrival 靜坐和你飛冇問題<br />\n畀少少時間文宣兄弟沖一沖散出面啲負面印象先<br />\n得唔得？"},{"pid":"92bd8